==English==

===Noun===

1.  A game where ping-pong balls are thrown at 10 cups (usually Solo brand) which are arranged in a triangular formation of base = 4 cups.  For each ball which is thrown into a cup the opposite team must drink the contents of said cup.  The first team to hit all 10 cups of the opposing team wins, and the losers must finish any remaining beer which is in the winners' cups.  

